  "detailed_description": "This is a short exciting hardcore puzzle-platform game about a <strong>lonely robot</strong>, which tries to find his master. To go all the way you'll have to look for the master in two dimensions at the same time. Parallel world module will help to overcome any obstacles! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/491010/extras/f9ab9aa8bfc6017d48b3bc0086658f8a.avif?t=1734374837\" width=618 height=108 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>unusual gameplay, travel through two worlds to reach the goal;<br></li><li>game possibilities increase as you progress through; <br></li><li>70 levels in five worlds; <br></li><li>a touching plot;<br></li><li>original soundtrack</li></ul>",
